ass=m><span class=title> PDA-Which one...?</span><hr size=1> I'm looking to buy a PDA for my g/f for Christmas but I know jack and shit about them...  Pocket PC's are a lil too steep for me I think...I'm looking for a PDA PREFERRABLY 200 or less...but if there is none then i'll move up some..<br>
